        <Parent_String>Western sigillata [300107380], Terra sigillata (pottery style) [300107376], Roman pottery styles [300107361], ancient Italian pottery styles [300107355], Ancient Italian [300107304], Mediterranean (Early Western World) [300020058], Early Western World [300019255], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
